title: Business Development Opportunities
body:
Harvest should cultivate strategic business relationships outside of the token economy with forward thinking start-ups to bolster branding and give itself a completive edge over others in the marketplace connecting with Gen-X,Y,Z and millennials.

An _example_  shared on Discord would be indoor farming.
-  https://ifarm.fi/
